CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

January 19, 2011

[Cite as 01/19/2011 Case Announcements, 2011-Ohio-19.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2010-1400. [State ex rel.] Lundeen v. Ryan.

Franklin App. No. 08AP-601. On appellee’s motion to strike the appeal and dismiss the cause and appellant’s motion in opposition. Motion to dismiss granted. Cause dismissed.

O’Connor, C.J., and Lundberg Stratton, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, Cupp, and McGee Brown, JJ., concur. Pfeifer, J., dissents.
